# Telco Customer Churn Prediction 🚀

## 📌 Overview

End-to-end Machine Learning pipeline to predict customer churn using the Telco dataset.

## ⚙️ Pipeline Stages

* Phase 1: EDA
* Phase 2: Feature Engineering
* Phase 3: Model Training (SVM best)
* Phase 4: Automated Pipeline
* Phase 5: Power BI Dashboard

## 🧠 Model Performance

* Best Model: SVM
* Accuracy: ~74%
* AUC: ~0.81

## 📊 Business Insights

* Month-to-month contracts → highest churn
* Fiber optic users → high risk
* High monthly charges → higher churn

## 🛠 Tech Stack

Python, Pandas, NumPy, Scikit-learn, Power BI, Git

## 🚀 Run Project

python run_all.py
